---
// 首屏英雄区块：承载品牌主标语、行动按钮、社交背书与主视觉。
// 视觉图与头像目前为占位样式，便于在设计资源完成后直接替换。
---

<!-- 首屏区域：作为用户进入首页后首先看到的品牌营销模块。 -->
<section class="hero">
  <div class="hero-container">
    <!-- 左侧文案区：包含主标题、中文副标题、品牌描述和主要行动按钮。 -->
    <div class="hero-content">
      <h2 class="hero-title">Step into <span class="italic">Curves</span><span class="asterisk">*</span></h2>
      <p class="hero-subtitle">踏出曲线的自由感</p>
      <p class="hero-description">
        LIMOVA 用设计表达态度。<br>
        每一双鞋，都是舒适与玩趣的结合。<br>
        你的享乐，自成曲线。
      </p>
      <button class="shop-btn">
        <span>SHOP NOW</span>
        <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
          <line x1="5" y1="12" x2="19" y2="12"></line>
          <polyline points="12 5 19 12 12 19"></polyline>
        </svg>
      </button>

      <div class="testimonials">
        <div class="avatars">
          <div class="avatar"></div>
          <div class="avatar"></div>
          <div class="avatar"></div>
          <div class="avatar-plus">+</div>
        </div>
        <p><strong>10099</strong> Happy Customers</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- 右侧视觉区：当前使用占位图和圆形徽章营造商品主视觉层次。 -->
    <div class="hero-visual">
      <div class="hero-image"></div>
      <div class="badge">
        <p>Comfy<br>But Make It<br>Fashion ✨</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  
  <div class="hero-shape"></div>
</section>

<style>
  /* 组件样式：负责首屏布局、按钮动效、头像叠放和响应式尺寸调整。 */
  .hero {
    position: relative;
    background-color: var(--light-bg);
    padding: 4rem 2rem;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .hero-container {
    max-width: 1400px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 4rem;
    align-items: center;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 2;
  }

  .hero-content {
    padding-right: 2rem;
  }

  .hero-title {
    font-size: 4.5rem;
    line-height: 1.1;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    font-weight: 700;
  }

  .italic {
    font-style: italic;
  }

  .asterisk {
    font-size: 2rem;
  }

  .hero-subtitle {
    font-size: 1rem;
    color: var(--dark-text);
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .hero-description {
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .shop-btn {
    background-color: var(--primary-purple);
    color: white;
    padding: 0.9rem 2.5rem;
    border-radius: 50px;
    font-weight: 600;
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.8rem;
    margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
  }

  .shop-btn:hover {
    background-color: #a682c5;
    transform: translateX(5px);
  }

  .testimonials {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 1rem;
  }

  .avatars {
    display: flex;
    position: relative;
    width: 100px;
  }

  .avatar {
    width: 40px;
    height: 40px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background-color: var(--gray-placeholder);
    border: 2px solid white;
    position: absolute;
  }

  .avatar:nth-child(1) {
    left: 0;
    z-index: 3;
  }

  .avatar:nth-child(2) {
    left: 25px;
    z-index: 2;
  }

  .avatar:nth-child(3) {
    left: 50px;
    z-index: 1;
  }

  .avatar-plus {
    width: 40px;
    height: 40px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background-color: var(--primary-purple);
    color: white;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    font-weight: 700;
    position: absolute;
    left: 75px;
    font-size: 1.2rem;
  }

  .testimonials p {
    margin-left: 120px;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
  }

  .hero-visual {
    position: relative;
    height: 500px;
  }

  .hero-image {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    background-color: var(--gray-placeholder);
    border-radius: 20px;
  }

  .badge {
    position: absolute;
    bottom: 20px;
    right: 20px;
    width: 120px;
    height: 120px;
    border: 3px solid var(--primary-purple);
    border-radius: 50%;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    background-color: white;
    text-align: center;
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  .badge p {
    line-height: 1.3;
  }

  .hero-shape {
    position: absolute;
    bottom: -50px;
    right: -100px;
    width: 400px;
    height: 400px;
    background-color: rgba(184, 157, 219, 0.1);
    border-radius: 50%;
    z-index: 1;
  }

  @media (max-width: 1024px) {
    .hero-container {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 2rem;
    }

    .hero-title {
      font-size: 3rem;
    }

    .hero-visual {
      height: 350px;
    }

    .hero-content {
      padding-right: 0;
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .hero {
      padding: 2rem 1rem;
    }

    .hero-title {
      font-size: 2rem;
    }

    .hero-visual {
      height: 250px;
    }
  }
</style>
